WEBVTT

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:32.015
A: That may be true, but you do like
more outgoing things than I do.

00:08:32.039 --> 00:08:34.535
AG: That's because
you're more introverted than I am.

00:08:34.559 --> 00:08:35.775
A: Right.

00:08:35.799 --> 00:08:38.535
(Music)

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:40.936
AG: You can laugh
about these kinds of differences

00:08:40.960 --> 00:08:42.296
with family and friends,

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:44.680
but they can be
pretty awkward in your job.

00:08:45.760 --> 00:08:47.536
To work well with other people,

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:51.856
you need to understand their personalities
and they need to understand yours.

00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:54.176
That requires a common vocabulary,

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:58.016
a language for talking about personality
that everyone speaks.

00:08:58.040 --> 00:09:00.216
Enter personality tests.